01:35:06.967 --> 01:35:09.356
Will come true for me

01:35:14.887 --> 01:35:17.117
My American dream

01:35:18.087 --> 01:35:20.317
For all to see

01:35:20.527 --> 01:35:22.483
William! In here.

01:35:22.567 --> 01:35:25.639
Every woman and man

01:35:26.127 --> 01:35:29.164
Has their own destiny

01:35:32.927 --> 01:35:35.964
To dream American Dreamz

